==Arabic==

===Letter===
'''ت'''

# The third letter of the [[Arabic]] language.

===Pronunciation===
''''taa'''' normally, i.e. when used in isolation.

NOTE: the letter ''''t'''' of ''''taa'''' is produced ''unfilled'' rather than ''filled''.

sounds '''taa''' when takes ''Fathah''

sounds '''ti''' when takes ''Kasra''

sounds '''tu''' when takes ''Damma''